title: Type O Negative - Symphony for the Devil [2006]
description:
Type O Negative - Symphony for the Devil [2006] DVD Rip

Symphony For The Devil is the first Live DVD of the legendary Type O Negative, featuring Pete Steele. The Live DVD features a concert filmed at the Bizarre Festival in Germany 1999, with an awe-inspiring 5.1 sound mix. Bonus features include an audio CD Single with a Santana medley, behind the scenes footage, interviews with band members, photo history of the band, commentary with band members, bios and more.

Video info: XviD - 464x352 - 29.97fps - 1h 44mn 7s 275ms
